org.webcurator.domain.model.core
Class HarvestResource

java.lang.Object
  org.webcurator.domain.model.core.HarvestResource
Direct Known Subclasses:
ArcHarvestResource
public class HarvestResource
extends java.lang.Object

A HarvestResource is a resource that has been harvested. It may be subclassed to provide additional functionality such as that required to support resources within ARC files. All Quality Review tools should ideally work with HarvestResource objects rather than their subclasses, though this may not always be possible.
